	</div>

	<div id="t_153_9" style="position: absolute; left: 10.29%; top: 31.68%;" class="c_153_6">
		mixed, tossed, and stretched the dough. The
	</div>

	<div id="t_153_10" style="position: absolute; left: 10.29%; top: 33.57%;" class="c_153_6">
