	</div>

	<div id="t_153_24" style="position: absolute; left: 9.97%; top: 48.96%;" class="c_153_6">
		money for one pair. Should you pick the electric blue
	</div>

	<div id="t_153_25" style="position: absolute; left: 9.97%; top: 50.85%;" class="c_153_6">
		sneakers or the sensible boots that will not go out of
	</div>

	<div id="t_153_26" style="position: absolute; left: 9.97%; top: 52.75%;" class="c_153_6">
		style? Whenever you make a choice you are actually
	</div>

	<div id="t_153_27" style="position: absolute; left: 9.97%; top: 54.64%;" class="c_153_6">
