	</div>

	<div id="t_153_28" style="position: absolute; left: 9.97%; top: 56.54%;" class="c_153_6">
		thing, you are choosing <span class="c_153_9">not</span><span class="c_153_8"> to do something else. What you</span>
	</div>

	<div id="t_153_29" style="position: absolute; left: 9.97%; top: 58.43%;" class="c_153_6">
		choose <span class="c_153_9">not</span><span class="c_153_8"> to do is your </span><span class="c_153_10">opportunity cost</span><span class="c_153_8">.</span>
	</div>

	<div id="t_153_30" style="position: absolute; left: 58.52%; top:51.08%;" class="c_153_11">
		?<span class="c_153_12">?</span>
